snippet.textDisplay:
Can I ask something? I wanted a Teddy Fresh necklace so bad, especially the silver necklace. I have Cystic Fibrosis and can't work, so I was saving the money that I dit get for quite a long time so that I could buy it when I had all the money together.
I was in the hospital for weeks and I was very sick, I'm on the transplant list for new lungs so I missed my opportunity to buy it because it's sold out now.
Will the CUBAN CHAIN NECKLACE be refilled at one point? And can I maybe buy it upfront? Because I'm in the hospital a lot and I'm really scared that if it will be refilled, I'm going to miss it again.
I'm really not looking for sympathy, I just want to explain my situation.
Maybe someone knows a specific day when it will be refilled, and if I could know that day I can put it in my agenda and if I would be in the hospital I could one of my parents ask if they would want to buy it for me. That would really help.
I hope I don't come across like I'm searching for sympathy because that's not what I mean at all and I'm really sorry if I do come across like that, I really don't mean to. I just wanted that necklace for so long. I saw Hila wearing it a long time ago on their podcast and since then I wanted it.
I love you guys so much, I hope you understand that I'm not trying to get sympathy I'm just really gutted that I missed it because I was too sick.

snippet.textDisplay: Hi Ethan and Hila! A lot of doctors are using infrared saunas as part of treatment for people with compromised immune systems. A real infrared sauna is going to cost you thousands and thousands of dollars, where as the portable one can fit almost anywhere, it easy to use, and most importantly it’s waaaaaay less expensive. So while I totally understand this seems like an incredibly strange product, it’s actually been quite the lifesaver for us immunocompromised/chronically ill! Hope this helped explain why that product existed lol!
